---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About The Wine Guide"
  description="We're wine enthusiasts who believe good advice shouldn't require a sommelier certificate."
>
  <div class="max-w-[42rem] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-[2rem] font-bold text-primary leading-tight">About The Wine Guide</h1>

    <div class="prose mt-8">
      <p>
        The Wine Guide exists because wine advice is usually terrible. It's either too simple ("just drink what you like!") or too pretentious ("note the tertiary aromas of leather and tobacco"). Neither is actually helpful.
      </p>
      <p>
        We write for people who want to drink better wine without spending years studying it. That means real recommendations at real price points, honest opinions, and explanations that treat you like an adult.
      </p>
      <h2>Our approach</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Every recommendation is based on real tasting, not PR samples or sponsor pressure.</li>
        <li>We state our opinions directly. If a wine is overrated, we say so.</li>
        <li>We explain the why behind every recommendation so you can make your own judgements.</li>
        <li>Price matters. Most of our guides focus on wines under $30.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Some links on this site are affiliate links. We earn a small commission if you buy through them, at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the lights on. We only link to products we'd actually recommend to a friend.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
